================================================================================
TSACI - HOW TO RUN THE APPLICATION
================================================================================

‚úÖ BACKEND IS ALREADY RUNNING (XAMPP Apache + MySQL)

================================================================================
OPTION 1: RUN ON MOBILE (iOS/Android) - RECOMMENDED
================================================================================

Mobile apps don't have CORS issues and work perfectly!

For iOS Simulator:
  flutter run

For Android Emulator:
  flutter run

For Physical Device:
  flutter run

Note: Make sure the device can reach your computer's IP address
Update API URL in lib/core/constants/api_constants.dart if needed:
  - For real device: Use your computer's local IP (e.g., http://192.168.1.100/tsaci/backend/api)
  - For simulator/emulator: Use http://127.0.0.1/tsaci/backend/api

================================================================================
OPTION 2: RUN ON WEB (Chrome with disabled security)
================================================================================

Flutter Web has CORS restrictions. To run in development:

Method A - Use the provided script:
  ./run_web.sh

Method B - Manual command:
  flutter run -d chrome --web-browser-flag "--disable-web-security" --web-browser-flag "--user-data-dir=/tmp/flutter-chrome"

‚ö†Ô∏è  WARNING: Only use this in development! Never browse other sites with this Chrome instance.

================================================================================
OPTION 3: RUN ON DESKTOP (macOS/Windows/Linux)
================================================================================

Desktop apps work perfectly without CORS issues!

For macOS:
  flutter run -d macos

For Windows:
  flutter run -d windows

For Linux:
  flutter run -d linux

