CHECKING BACKEND STATUS
================================================================================

Test backend is running:
  cd backend
  php test_api.php

View backend logs:
  php backend/view_logs.php

Check API endpoint:
  curl http://127.0.0.1/tsaci/backend/api/products

================================================================================
CONSOLE LOGGING
================================================================================

Both backend and frontend now have unified logging!

Backend Logs:
  - Location: backend/logs/tsaci.log
  - View: php backend/view_logs.php

Frontend Logs:
  - Printed to Flutter console
  - Shows all API requests/responses
  - Shows authentication attempts
  - Shows sync operations

